ive been thinking. 
 -wow thats a new one
 im starting to miss the way we all used to hang out
 when i went to shasta, we always hung out during lunch
  from playing guitars in highways, to fixing drama, we always had somthing to do
 hanging out after school
 all that good stuff you know
 and it really gets to me, cause we all used to be soo fucking close
 some of us more then others, but we all seemed to get along, like a family
 
 its all really starting to get to me cause i look back and i was so happy and everyone else is too well most of the times anyways
 i miss all the good times, i miss sneeking off campus to go smoke pot at the river trail
 i miss all my freinds i had, and lost when i got kicked out
 i miss hanging out with manda during p.e and just talking about life with her
 i miss getting excited just so i could see chelsea in between periods
 i miss getting detention in math every day for absoluty no reason except i wouldnt stop talking to annie
 i miss doing all the shit that we did when we knew we were going to get into trouble but just didnt give a fuck cause we were all having fun TOGETHER
  and i miss ALL the good times weve had together
 i just wish i could have gone back and fixed it to where we never fell apart like we are now
 id do anything to have that life back
 and its sad to know that it most likely is never going to happen
 ......-JUST ANOTHER RAMBLE

      its funny cause im writing this down thinking that "maybe someone has advice" or somthing like that. 

      But i know that no one can fix my emptyness, the hole inside of me, there is no way to fill it so i will eventually have to get over it, but its already been this long so maybe i wont get over it, maybe ill have this hole forever. 
i dont know its very depressing and im sick of being depressed over the same fucking thing , its stupid and rediculous, completley absurd..............wtf am i writing this down for??! no one cares -im out
